     8→ * 3. Run bun install --production (compiles native modules fresh)
     9→ * 4. Native modules (like better-sqlite3 from claude-agent-sdk) will be 
    10→ *    rebuilt by electron-builder for Electron's Node ABI
    11→ * 
    12→ * Output: packages/ui/server-bundle/
    13→ */
